Package org.jmisb.api.klv.eg0104 Description

EG 0104.5 "Predator UAV Basic Universal Metadata Set".

This implementation only supports data extraction. We intentionally do not support creating this metadata message, because it is obsolete. Its also quite inefficient. We suggest (as at 2020) using ST0601 instead.
